title: MFD2 Navigation DVD Version 2013 V10 Volkswagen
description:
No more gaps: New roads, new residential areas and new traffic features means that Tele Atlas maps are now good for near perfect coverage in the majority of countries.

From anywhere to anywhere in no time at all: With even more house numbers now included, the Europe DVD 2013 EX offers detailed door-to-door navigation in every single country. Even entering your destination is easier with postcode searches enabled for most major areas.

Keep on driving: Avoid traffic jams and road works in a single bound with the latest in dynamic route guidance. The Europe DVD 2013 EX enables traffic info for a whole host of countries including Belgium, Denmark, France, Germany, Great Britain, Norway, Switzerland and many others.
